== 结构 ==
顶枕沟大部分区域位于[[大脑半球|大脑半球]]的内侧，只有少部分在外侧可见。

* 顶枕沟的外侧（右图1）位于大脑半球“枕极”（occipital pole）前的5厘米处，长约1.25厘米。
* 顶枕沟的内侧（右图2）向大脑半球内部纵深，与[[距状沟|距状沟]]相连，位于[[胼胝体|胼胝体]]后部。<ref name=":0" />

== 功能 ==
许多[[神经成像|神经成像]]研究显示，顶枕沟与{{le|背外侧前额叶皮层|Dorsolateral prefrontal cortex}}一同参与人脑的计划/规划（planning）活动。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Planning and Spatial Working Memory: a Positron Emission Tomography Study in Humans|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/abs/10.1111/j.1460-9568.1996.tb01219.x|last=Owen|first=Adrian M.|last2=Doyon|first2=Julien|date=1996|journal=European Journal of Neuroscience|issue=2|doi=10.1111/j.1460-9568.1996.tb01219.x|volume=8|pages=353–364|language=en|issn=1460-9568|last3=Petrides|first3=Michael|last4=Evans|first4=Alan C.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Neural systems engaged by planning: a PET study of the Tower of London task|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/0028393295001336|date=1996-06-01|journal=Neuropsychologia|issue=6|doi=10.1016/0028-3932(95)00133-6|volume=34|pages=515–526|language=en|issn=0028-3932}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Neural correlates of planning ability: Frontal lobe activation during the tower of London test|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/0028393293901048|date=1993-12-01|journal=Neuropsychologia|issue=12|doi=10.1016/0028-3932(93)90104-8|volume=31|pages=1367–1378|language=en|issn=0028-3932}}</ref>

